  <brief_title>Effect of Usage of Electroencephalogram (EEG) Entropy on the Incidence of Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction in Geriatric Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Is the Ese of EEG Entropy as Intra-operative Monitor Improves Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
